QuestData.Title: Your First Mezzonic Protolock
QuestData.Description: In order to aid me in my research, you will need to decode various Progenitor cyphers like the Mezzonic Protolock. Now, I will show you what you need to do.
QuestData.RewardText:
Use this knowledge and collect more data from the field, Maw Walker.
There is still one more Cache of Creation that I must instruct you on.
